            - citation-twoiaf-targaryen
            - citation-agot-appendix
        confidence: high
        status: accepted
        notes: "Verified against TWOIAF, The Targaryen Kings section. Source text: The eldest was Aegon, born in the Red Keep in 135 AC after Viserys's return from Lys. He was a robust lad who grew to be handsome and charming, and also irresponsible and capricious"
